<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/386401AGKNTQBGJPRPVDKCPNRMJGBVPJV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "3rd Annual Hits for Heritage ft. Chilliwack";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/9c53fcc4-eab3-42fb-ba87-7b33904af3fe.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Central Okanagan Heritage Society presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">3rd ANNUAL HITS FOR HERITAGE</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">featuring Chilliwack's Farewell Tour</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The Central Okanagan Heritage Society, in partnership with What's On Events, present the 3rd Annual Hits for Heritage Fundraiser! Enjoy Chilliwack’s Farewell to Friends Tour, with the Ryan Donn Band kicking off the night. It’s set to be a lively evening of rock, community spirit, and raising funds to keep our heritage alive!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come sing along to the songs you love! “Fly At Night,” “California Girl,” “My Girl (Gone Gone Gone),” “Lonesome Mary,” “Whatcha Gonna Do” and more.  Join Legendary Canadian rock band Chilliwack for an evening of music & memories as they hit the road for the last time in their 55-year history.  Chilliwack’s Farewell to Friends Tour began in 2025, and continues into 2026, hitting more stops across the country. As one fan said recently: “They sounded exactly the same, I couldn’t believe it!  The energy, the high notes, all the good songs. Sooooo worth it!” - Robert C. 2025<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The band has produced 12 albums, numerous hits, and received 15 gold and platinum albums making them one of the Greatest Canadian bands of all time. Their live album “There and Back” continues to win over a whole new generation of fans, showcasing Chilliwack’s dynamic and electrifying live performances of the hit songs we all know and love. Come join in the fun before this farewell tour is gone, gone, gone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The 3rd Annual Hits for Heritage Fundraiser is not just a concert</span></span>—this night at the Kelowna Community Theatre promises high energy, nostalgia, and a powerful purpose! There will be a <span class=\"BoldText\">silent auction, a 50/50 raffle and lots of ways to support our growing non-profit!</span> Many local businesses have donated awesome items and packages for our silent auction, we couldn't do it without our community and volunteers! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $79.00</span>  ($66.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Hits For Heritage</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
