<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/397001ABVQMVHGBKTCJCSQKLQMTLCMKCM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Midsummer Night's Dream - A 90's Musical";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/0018213f-018f-4a73-8833-589d81b92199.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>New Vintage Theatre Company presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">A MIDSUMMER NIGHT'S DREAM</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">A 90's Musical</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Shakespeare's classic comedy gets transported into the 1990's for an epic musical that is a hilarious comedy for all ages. Performed by New Vintage Theatre's famous summer teen acting program, you don't want to miss the dreamy Midsummer Night's Dream. It will be the highlight of your summer!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior (65+)  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">A Midsummer Night's Dream - A 90's Musical</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
