<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/390801AKLKGPKMHQRKDBLLTLRRBCHSCJJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Adventurers, Wanderers, & Explorers Film Festival";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/808298bc-2e47-49a1-9a28-2d277c961061.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Adventurers, Wanderers, & Explorers Film Society presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ADVENTURERS, WANDERERS, & EXPLORERS FILM FESTIVAL</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The Adventurers, Wanderers, and Explorers Film Festival is a celebration of the true spirit of adventure, from mountain culture through to sea culture and beyond. Our goal is to promote an understanding and appreciation of our cherished and wild outdoor spaces by creating opportunities for intrepid soles to share experiences and inspiration in a safe and welcoming venue.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior/Child  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - 65+, Child under 12</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Adventurers, Wanderers, & Explorers Film Festival</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
