<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/330401APJDBJDDDLJDCMVLTJLJTDVTTPJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Afrikaans is Lekker";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/84c69195-7378-45f0-b853-04ff9a5e8081.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>South African Events presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">AFRIKAANS IS LEKKER</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A celebration of South African music in Canada. Every year we bring the best Afrikaans artists to Canada. 2026 is the first time that we are performing in Kelowna and will be including three of the best artists from South Africa. Kurt Darren, Elandre and Refentse will ensure that it is awesome night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $100.46</span>  ($85.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $13.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2 Adult  $88.96</span>  ($75.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $11.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2 Child  $60.21</span>  ($50.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.85 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3 Adult  83.21</span>  ($70.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.85 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3 Child  $48.71</span>  ($40.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Afrikaans is Lekker</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
