		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Experience an unforgettable evening with Hustinder as he brings his Bhadaur to Abroad Tour to Kelowna this summer. Enjoy a high-energy live performance featuring his hit songs, backed by a full band and vibrant stage production. Join us for a night of Punjabi music, culture, and community celebration at the theatre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $82.86</span>  ($70.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $54.11</span>  ($45.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP  $105.86</span>  ($90.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $13.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Bhadaur to Abroad</span> applicable ticket fees are non-refundable.</span>
