<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/363001AQTGLVHHMTQLGRLKTKRNPCGBRKS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CMK - James Ehnes & Andrew Armstrong";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b172f769-3131-4631-b36b-6f315ecbc129.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Chamber Music Kelowna presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">JAMES EHNES, violin & ANDREW ARMSTRONG, piano</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Internationally celebrated violinist James Ehnes joins acclaimed pianist Andrew Armstrong for an evening of exceptional artistry and musical partnership. Canadian-born Ehnes is one of today’s most sought-after violinists, performing regularly with leading orchestras  and winner of Grammy awards and recipient of multiple Gramophone and Juno Awards.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Armstrong is internationally admired for his passionate expression and dazzling technique. He has appeared in major venues, performing more than sixty concertos with orchestra and collaborating with leading ensembles worldwide. Longtime recital partners, they have produced recordings of the works by Franck, Strauss, Bartók, and the complete Beethoven violin sonatas. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $67.50</span>  ($56.34 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.80 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student (w/ID)  $25.00</span>  ($19.38 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.26 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">James Ehnes & Andrew Armstrong</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
