<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360001AKKMKNBBVGVSKMPQPCHQSRSHMGG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Desi Junction Music Festival";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/702231a9-6417-4e6f-86db-badabecb33c0.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">DESI JUNCTION MUSIC FESTIVAL</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>DESI JUNCTION MUSIC FESTIVAL is an amazing charity event who's mission is to help raise awareness for local non-profit organizations through the music and dance of India!!! This year we will be adding new entertainment to the line up!! With talented singers, dancers, rappers, up-and-coming talent will be adding and returning, we have an amazing kidz zone fun for all ages, food trucks to enjoy and well-needed fundraisers for our local non-profit charity and much more to explore....We recommend getting your tickets early!! Limited Space @ Rutland Centennial Park!! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>YOU DON'T WANNA MISS THIS EPIC EVENT!!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Gate opens at 1:00 pm, entertainment begins at 2:00 pm<span><br/></span>Last performers take the stage at 9:00 pm<span><br/></span>Gate closes at 8:30 pm <span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">The schedule and gate closing are subject to change.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>kidz zone runs 1 - 4 pm<span><br/></span>Main stage opens at 2 pm with announcements<span><br/></span>Dancers go on at 2:30 pm<span><br/></span>Local artist open the stage at 3:00 pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Music from:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>HEADLINING ARTISTS</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li> DEEP JANDU</li><li> ROACH KILLA</li></ul><span><br/></span><h2>MAIN ARTISTS</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li> SHV  (rmg)</li><li> MONICO SANTANA</li><li> MINISTER MUSIC</li><li> DJHEER</li><li> JAGGA  WORLDWIDE /GKRAZY/ MONEYONYOURMIND & ARBAJ KAHLON,</li><li> MerzaMusic, 40k, Shally rehal, TBM </li><li> GUNNER</li><li> MEET SINGH</li></ul><span><br/></span>Local artists: Gold Money, Meja, A.S.M.M, Himrose Shah (Hamy), Harrie J.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information about the event, artists and schedule: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.desijunctionfestival.com/\">desijunctionfestival.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">EARLY BIRD PRICING <span class=\"UnderlineText\">AVAILABLE UNTIL AUGUST 4TH</span>!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $57.50</span>  ($50.00 base price + $7.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 12 and under are free, but still require a ticket</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">GENERAL ADMISSION PRICING <span class=\"UnderlineText\">AVAILABLE AUGUST 5TH - 31ST</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $97.75</span>  ($85.00 base price + $12.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 12 and under are free, but still require a ticket</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">LAST CHANCE PRICING <span class=\"UnderlineText\">AVAILABLE SEPTEMBER 1ST - 12TH</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $138.00</span>  ($120.00 base price + $18.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 12 and under are free, but still require a ticket</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Desi Junction Music Festival</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
