<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360801AJTKRDCBJLBLRLHMPGJTGHNTVVH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Flip Flop Gala";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/92f5b45c-0119-4ea6-8648-863b355b0943.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Touchdown Kelowna presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">FLIP FLOP GALA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Where Black Tie Meets Barefoot</span></span></h2>An exclusive, one-night-only social dining experience set against the backdrop of Kelowna’s waterfront, the <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span> blends elevated style with relaxed Okanagan energy — deliberately breaking the rules of what a gala can be.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Already secured your tickets and are planning for event day?<span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/flip-flop-gala-know-you-go\">View the Know Before You Go</a> for details on parking, arrival times, prohibited items, and more.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Designed for those who appreciate contrast, the evening brings together polished presentation and laid‑back confidence — refinement without pretence, luxury without formality.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guests are immersed directly in the experience, moving through curated spaces that encourage connection, conversation, and discovery. There are no assigned tables, no formal program, and no separation between VIP and guest — just a fluid, social atmosphere designed for interaction.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At its core, this is a social night out centred around food, atmosphere, and shared experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guests mingle freely, from the dance floor to bespoke cabana‑style lounge spaces designed for conversation, connection, and people‑watching.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">An intentionally limited experience.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Your ticket includes:<span><br/></span><ul><li>A welcome cocktail on arrival by <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://luckhurstfarm.com/\">Luckhurst Farm &amp; Distillery</a></li><li>Elevated food grazing stations showcasing local flavours by Chef Rod Butters' <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://theokanagantable.com/\">The Okanagan Table</a></li><li>A continuous soundtrack by Vancouver's DJ Pri</li><li>Lounge-style seating and open gathering spaces designed for social interaction</li></ul>Additional beverages will be available for purchase throughout the evening.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With intentionally limited capacity, the <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span> is designed to feel intimate, comfortable, and distinctly different from larger festival events. Entry is exclusively available through corporate packages or limited tickets via theboxoffice.ca.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional information</span><span><br/></span><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">19+ event</span></li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Gates open at 7:00 pm</span></li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Themed attire encouraged</span> (confidence required — there’s no wrong interpretation)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Rain or shine</span> — the setting shapes the mood either way</li></ul>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">General  $181.13</span>  ($157.50 base price + $23.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-29T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/92f5b45c-0119-4ea6-8648-863b355b0943.jpg>;
