<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/367001AKKQVDCDBPVCMRJJSMPBCPLQLSB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "KCCA - JoyRide";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/ccd9fe18-8857-4dd1-b9cc-9a4663039be6.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Community Concert Association presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">JOYRIDE</span></h1><h2>KCCA 2026-2027 Series</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>With spring in the air, jump in the ragtop and let a pair of shimmering talents take you on the ultimate JoyRide! On piano, Mark Camilleri boasts a career working with such luminaries as The Tenors, Andrea Bocelli and Céline Dion. Colin Maier, a former stuntman and acrobat, enchants on oboe, vocals and musical saw. Buckle up for a ride both entertaining and joyful!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Website:  <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.joyrideconcerts.com\">joyrideconcerts.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This concert is part of the Kelowna Community Concert Association’s 2026/2027 season, composed of five world-class concerts. The subscription price is uniquely affordable and the best way to secure a ticket to this show.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/kelowna-community-concert-association\">Find full details on the season and the subscription here.</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Single tickets for this concert will be available in very limited quantities a minimum of two weeks prior to the concert. Prices for individual tickets will vary.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">JoyRide</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
