<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/367401AKVLPMCTVKNSVVRGCRVRQTPKTQC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "KCCA - Piano Heist";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b2c53d01-425a-4827-bf24-f5ba0e90fe55.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Community Concert Association presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">PIANO HEIST</span></h1><h2>KCCA 2026-2027 Series</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Lifelong buddies Nico Rhodes and Patrick Courtin grew up travelling the world, steeped in music and theatre. One day they’re shocked to learn that the piano had fallen from favour! They ride to the rescue with Piano Heist: Keys are the Champions!, an enchanting new tapestry of classical masterpieces, vibrant boogie-woogie, romantic ballads, and epic ’80s-style synth battles, woven together with humour and audience engagement. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Website: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pianoheist.com\">pianoheist.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This concert is part of the Kelowna Community Concert Association’s 2026/2027 season, composed of five world-class concerts. The subscription price is uniquely affordable and the best way to secure a ticket to this show.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/kelowna-community-concert-association\">Find full details on the season and the subscription here.</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Single tickets for this concert will be available in very limited quantities a minimum of two weeks prior to the concert. Prices for individual tickets will vary.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Piano Heist</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
