<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/340001AGLJMLGPQTTPTCPRHLNGTCSTBNT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Magic Men Australia - Feel the Magic Tour";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/ea823324-e3f5-4fbe-bb81-9633a2a00033.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Magic Men Australia presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">FEEL THE MAGIC TOUR</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Featuring Will Parfitt</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience advisories: 19+ years of age, use of strobe lighting and smoke</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The #1 Ladies Night Out, Breaking Records Worldwide MagicMen Australia is taking over the world, breaking attendance records across Australia, New Zealand, Europe, U.S South America and Canada, including over 6,500 screaming ladies at a single Ladies Night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is global entertainment at its peak.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>And for the first time, the show presents TikTok and world-famous Instagram superstar Will Parfitt, with a combined following of over 20 million.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>He’s one of the most recognised male entertainers on social media… and he’s live on stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready for a night you’ll never forget.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>MagicMen delivers Australia’s most talented performers, high-energy choreography, jaw-dropping acrobatics, and cheeky crowd interaction, all packaged into a world-class touring production.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This isn’t just a show. It’s an experience. Expect:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>* Record-breaking performances across the globe<span><br/></span>* Featuring Will Parfitt (20M+ followers)<span><br/></span>* World-class dance routines<span><br/></span>* High-energy group numbers + unforgettable solos<span><br/></span>* Charisma, comedy & crowd interaction<span><br/></span>* A safe, inclusive, feel-good atmosphere<span><br/></span>* VIP meet & greet + photo opportunities<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether it’s a hens night, birthday, girls’ night, or a chance to escape reality, MagicMen delivers a night that’s classy, powerful, and completely unforgettable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>MagicMen Australia Where entertainment meets energy and where records keep getting broken.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Meet & Greet and Ticket Tier Access:</span></h2><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Ultra Premium, Premium and Deluxe</span> ticket holders will be granted early access to the venue at 6:30 PM, including a meet & greet upon entry.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>On-stage guest participation is primarily selected from the Premium and Deluxe ticket tiers.<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Regular ticket holders will be admitted at 7:00 PM.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultra Premium  $135.19</span>  ($115.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $17.33 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Premium  $121.90</span>  ($103.95 base price + $2.36 CIF + $15.59 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Deluxe  $105.00</span>  ($89.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $13.39 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $68.77</span>  ($57.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.66 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Magic Men Australia - Feel The Magic Tour</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
