		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Experience the thrill of Okanagan Sun football at the iconic Apple Bowl in Kelowna! Whether you’re a die-hard fan or new to the game, join us in cheering on the Sun as they chase another championship.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Note:</span><span><br/></span>Reserved seating is available in rows 2 to 9 of the main grandstand. Reminder of the main grandstand and east side bleachers are general admission<span><br/></span>Students must present a valid high school, UBC, or Okanagan College ID.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Game Day Details</span><span><br/></span>Venue: Apple Bowl, 1555 Burtch Road, Kelowna, BC<span><br/></span>Gates Open: 1 hour before kickoff<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Please Note:</span><span><br/></span>-All game dates and times are subject to change due to weather, smoke, or field availability.<span><br/></span>-If a game is rescheduled or cancelled, your ticket will be transferable to another regular season game.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join the Sun family and be part of the excitement! Let’s make this season unforgettable. Go Sun!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Reserved Seating</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">All ages: $20.00</span> ($17.37 + $2.63 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">General Admission</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult: $20.00</span> ($17.37 + $2.63 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student 13-18yrs: $15.00</span> ($12.37 + $2.63 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Seniors 65yrs+: $15.00</span> ($12.37 + $2.63 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Kids under 12: Free</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"> A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Tickets for Okanagan Sun Football and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
