<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/384001ADJCBJJJMLSDCLJMMLPJPGPBGDP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Opera Kelowna  - Mozart's The Marriage of Figaro";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/4e4f599a-576b-4ec7-989a-47d90936c515.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Opera Kelowna presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MOZART'S THE MARRIAGE OF FIGARO</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>It’s the big day for Susanna and Figaro, but everywhere they turn it’s a wedding disaster waiting to happen! One of their bosses is having a major– and justified–meltdown, and the other is hoping to sleep with the bride. The groom’s overdue debt comes calling, and then there’s the cousin who shows up everywhere… except where he is supposed to be! What makes this madcap story so special is W.A. Mozart blends the hi-jinx of a classic comedy with earnest, heartfelt, and even heartbreaking moments that the characters each take in their turn. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Opera Kelowna’s production of The Marriage of Figaro is set in the early 1800s on a European estate, while taking some important liberties with period-appropriate colour schemes. And with Wigs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The production is performed in Italian with English Subtitles, and live orchestra with an all Canadian cast. For full details visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.operakelowna.com/\">www.operakelowna.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span>Adult:<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1: $100.98</span> ($85.76 + $2.36 CIF + $12.86 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2: $89.32</span> ($75.62 + $2.36 CIF + $11.34 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3: $77.00</span> ($64.90 + $2.36 CIF + $9.74 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Senior (65+):<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1: $89.15</span> ($75.47 + $2.36 CIF + $11.32 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2: $78.89</span> ($66.55 + $2.36 CIF + $9.98 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3: $68.04</span> ($57.11 + $2.36 CIF + $8.57 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Student (under 18):<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1: $86.20</span> ($72.90 + $2.36 CIF + $10.94 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2: $76.28</span> ($64.28 + $2.36 CIF + $9.64 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3: $65.81</span> ($55.17 + $2.36 CIF + $8.28 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">*Limited Pay-What-You-Wish tickets available.</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> Pay-What-You-Wish tickets are available ranging from $5.00 - $30.00 in increments of $5.00. </li><li> $2.36 CIF and $1.05 + 5% Service Fee are added to each Pay-What-You-Wish ticket.</li></ul><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Opera Kelowna tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
