  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Orchestral Rock Odyssey";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/88d2db6b-9110-4501-8c35-3f8637b2ac97.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>The Gary Cable Foundation presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ORCHESTRAL ROCK ODYSSEY</span>  </h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">featuring the Gary Cable Project, the GCP Orchestra & Project Singers</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre - Saturday, September 26th & Sunday, September 27th</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Back by popular demand, the Gary Cable Project returns to rock the Okanagan with ORCHESTRAL ROCK ODYSSEY. Join us as we pump up the volume on a retro tribute to legendary artists and some of the most iconic music of all time, with spectacular new arrangements of classic hits by Genesis, Whitney Houston, Styx, Kansas, Simon & Garfunkel, Kansas, Elton John, the Beatles, Earth Wind & Fire, the Bee Gees, and a lot more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $84.75</span>  ($71.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $74.40</span>  ($62.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.40 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth  $41.05</span>  ($33.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.05 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $75.55</span>  ($63.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.55 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $65.20</span>  ($54.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.20 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth  $38.75</span>  ($31.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $43.36</span>  ($35.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.36 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $39.90</span>  ($32.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.90 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth  $36.45</span>  ($29.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.45 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Orchestral Rock Odyssey</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
