<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/377001AVDPSCGCGBNKCNQCHRDTKNHHLBV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 2 - A Musical Grand Tour (Kelowna)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/7305513b-e27b-45a8-82a2-1e49a0c1317d.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">A GRAND MUSICAL TOUR</span></h1><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">CONDUCTOR: Ivars Taurins</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Early Music specialist Ivars Taurins conducts the Okanagan Symphony Orchestra in this musical Grand Tour of 18th century Europe, guiding the audience through Germany, England, Italy, and France via the great Baroque masters. Taurins—long associated with the Tafelmusik Baroque Orchestra and Chamber Choir—has helped shape historically informed performance internationally, making him the ideal guide for this journey.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>--
<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Section A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $75.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $11.25 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$88.61</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $56.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.44 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$67.05</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $63.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.56 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$75.67</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.75 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$54.11</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65yrs+, Youth - up to age 24yrs.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">A Musical Grand Tour</span> tickets and applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
