  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 5 - Chopin & Beethoven (Kelowna)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/50fb385a-30e1-498c-8e0d-9a5e26542028.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">CHOPIN & BEETHOVEN</span></h1><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">CONDUCTOR: Monica Chen</span></h2><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">featuring Angela Yixuan Miao, piano</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Twelve-year-old prodigy Angela Yixuan Miao brings a lyricism and skill to Chopin’s Piano Concerto No. 2 that belies her young age. Conductor Monica Chen leads the Okanagan Symphony Orchestra in a program shaped by resilience and contrast: Beethoven’s dramatic Coriolan Overture, the buoyant charm of his Eighth Symphony, and Canadian composer Stephen Chatman’s beautiful Over Thorns to Stars.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>--
<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Section A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $75.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $11.25 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$88.61</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $56.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.44 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$67.05</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $63.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.56 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$75.67</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.75 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$54.11</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65yrs+, Youth - up to age 24yrs.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">Chopin & Beethoven</span> tickets and applicable 