  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Pavlo & Band In Concert";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b014cd0f-72aa-4a0a-92e2-d2ce174f5fd4.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Hejaz Entertainment Inc. presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">PAVLO & BAND IN CONCERT</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Internationally renowned, award-winning recording artist, performer and songwriter,<span><br/></span>Pavlo has become famous for bringing every audience to its feet. Pavlo, a true World Music Artist, returns to Kelowna with his world class band for an evening of Mediterranean inspired music.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Let the rhythms transport you to the sun soaked shores of Santorini as you experience Pavlo’s signature blend of Spanish, Greek, Rumba and Flamenco music in this vibrant feel good concert.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>OPA!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $65.96</span>  ($55.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP  $83.21</span>  ($70.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.85 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP seating includes a one hour Meet & Greet with Pavlo in front of the stage at 6:00pm</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Pavlo & Band In Concert</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
