<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/388401ALBTMPRHSSDKSQHJRQPTMKRKTKT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "RCA Presents - Maple Reserve";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/a56ed2f5-c057-445b-9827-e3a2bdd28c12.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Rotary Centre for the Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MAPLE RESERVE</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">with guest, D'Lite</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Maple Reserve is Canada’s finest a cappella quartet, performing works that range from classic to contemporary barbershop. Hailing from Toronto, these boys have been singing together since their early days at Earl Haig Secondary School and have grown into an internationally recognized group. Having performed in Canada, USA, the UK, Germany, and Sweden, Maple Reserve is no stranger to the world stage. Maple Reserve takes the opportunity to perform wherever, whenever, and strive to share the joy of music. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Maple Reserve</span><span><br/></span>Chris Tanaka-Mann<span><br/></span>Greg Mallett<span><br/></span>Jonah Lazar<span><br/></span>Reuven Grajner<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As an opening act, D’Lite, a dynamic and fun sextet and part of the White Sails a Cappella Chorus, brings rich harmony, and the joyful energy of women’s barbershop.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">D’Lite</span><span><br/></span>Bettina Garry<span><br/></span>Anita Bakker<span><br/></span>Renee Dow<span><br/></span>Hedy Brouwer<span><br/></span>Tanya Holdenried<span><br/></span>Paola Serravelli<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Maple Reserve will facilitate a community barbershop workshop on Saturday, April 3 from 10 – 11:30.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To learn more about Marple Reserve, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://maplereservequartet.com/\">maplereservequartet.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To learn more about White Sails Chorus, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://whitesailschorus.com/\">whitesailschorus.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Sponsored by Cristalina PARC.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $51.01</span>  ($42.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.65 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $32.90</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.29 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Maple Reserve</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
