<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/386201AVNGGPMJMRMPQGVNSNDJBRQRBBC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "RCA Presents - Oh Pray Tell";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/ab187479-9f8f-4b46-b065-d81e3b03fa02.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Rotary Centre for the Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">OH PRAY TELL</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Oh Pray Tell is a musical trio comprised of Betty Supple, Sally Titasey, and Shayna Jones. Their music features stunning three-part harmonies that are grounded in banjo and stomp-clap-cajon rhythms and carry poetry, stories, and spoken word. Oh Pray Tell offers up an original, soulful sound influenced by gospel, rhythm & blues, roots music and folk story-telling.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To learn more about Oh Pray Tell, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://ohpraytell.com/\">ohpraytell.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $44.98</span>  ($36.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.87 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $32.90</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.29 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Oh Pray Tell</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
