<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/389801ANRBGNHPGSHDGLTCPBJKNKHGGQP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "RCA Presents - Presto! by Nayana Fielkov";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/1406991c-4729-4f41-9d96-2408a2bc7a73.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Rotary Centre for the Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">PRESTO! by NAYANA FIELKOV</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Presto! The Great Lambrusco turns scarves into eggs! Coins appear from thin air, and a cupcake gets baked in a shoe! In this comedic unfolding, the audience finds out that illusions are not reality, and that to find true magic, we must slow down, observe, and listen.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Real magic, real comedy, and real entertainment for the whole family! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ideal for families with children ages 5 – 12.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Acclaimed performing artist Nayana Fielkov has performed at festivals and venues across the country with her genre-bending approach to theatre. She is co-creator of award-winning RAGMOP Theatre, Habitats, Underbelly, and The Myrtle Sisters, and is a founding member of the Dusty Flowerpot Cabaret.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Nayana will present a workshop on Saturday, May 1 from 10 to 11:30 am in the Sun FM studio. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To learn more about Nayana Fielkov, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.nayanafielkov.ca/\">nayanafielkov.ca</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $32.90</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.29 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $20.83</span>  ($15.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.72 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Presto! by Nayana Fielkov</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
