<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/388801AHKGCGHKHTPSKLHVGKJQKRQKSMB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "RCA Presents - Tamar Ilana & Ventanas";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/04ebf7ed-0294-4b35-b618-f795299669d4.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Rotary Centre for the Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">TAMAR ILANA & VENTANAS</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Tamar Ilana & Ventanas is a 6-piece global music and flamenco band based in Toronto, Canada. Founded in 2011 by \"powerhouse vocalist\" (Downbeat Magazine) and Jewish-Indigenous vocalist/dancer Tamar Ilana, they've received 4 CFMA nominations, and toured across Canada, the US, Colombia, Portugal, Ireland and Spain. They released their 4th album, AZADI, in 2024: original compositions that reflect on life’s freedoms with strong influences from their unique combination of cultural and musical backgrounds including Flamenco, Sephardic, Balkan, Greek, Turkish, Jazz, Pop, Classical and Mediterranean folk. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"Tamar has spent a lifetime mastering beautiful vocal traditions from around the world, only to arrive at a sound that is uniquely her own. She transcends genre, geography, and language. She is Canada’s own pan-global diva.\" - Jesse Cook <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"Tamar has a power in her performance that is completely joyful and transportive. Her singing and dancing are deeply naturalistic and she’s transfixed me with her capacity to unravel a song. I’m a huge admirer.\" - Leslie Feist<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To learn more about Tamar Ilana & Ventanas, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.ventanasmusic.com/\">ventanasmusic.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $54.64</span>  ($45.15 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.13 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $32.90</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.29 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Tamar Ilana & Ventanas</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
