<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/392201AHTSMMSPTGHNHJKBCKGJMDLMBKS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sadé Awele Live at the Mary Irwin Theatre";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/953bd371-59d9-4088-9ecb-b8e62e6f57ec.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Awele Entertainment presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SADÉ AWELE LIVE AT THE MARY IRWIN THEATRE</span></h1><h2>with special guest Gracie Field</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join Western Canadian Music Award Winner, Sadé Awele, for an unforgettable evening of music, storytelling, and soul. Blending Afrosoul, Afropop, and R&B with influences from her Nigerian roots, Sadé creates a powerful live experience that is both intimate and uplifting. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audiences can expect heartfelt originals, rich vocals, and a celebration of culture, resilience, and connection. Known for her captivating vocals and emotionally rich songwriting, Sadé’s music bridges continents and cultures, delivering an experience that moves both heart and body. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss this special live performance. Through powerful vocals, heartfelt storytelling, and infectious rhythms, Sadé invites audiences into a musical journey of joy, reflection, and connection.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult Early Bird discount</span> $3.00 (automatically applied) until July 20<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $23.41</span>  ($18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.05 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $14.99</span>  ($10.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes.  <span class=\"BoldText\">Sadé Awele</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
