<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/369401AJTSKCHLJHSDVLCRTBKCRSKLQHN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Steve Hofstetter";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/240c0d0d-776c-44ad-8d5f-e0e5f79151f3.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Steve Hofstetter presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">STEVE HOFSTETTER</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This event is for ages 14+ only.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>One of the world's most popular comedians with billions of views on his videos, Steve Hofstetter returns to Kelowna with an all-new set. He’s sold out shows in hundreds of cities and dozens of countries. Now is your chance to find out what the fuss is about during this no-holds-barred stand-up performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Front Row  $259.92</span>  ($223.65 base price + $2.36 CIF + $33.90 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Gold  $77.58</span>  ($65.10 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.12 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Silver  $53.43</span>  ($44.10 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.97 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Front Row ticket includes:</span></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>Meet & Greet 30 minutes prior to show (5:30pm), </li><li>autographed book, </li><li>audio book, </li><li>and all 8 of Steve's albums.</li></ul><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Steve Hofstetter</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
