  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Summer Nights Gala";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/34c06f7f-3f2c-43cf-b338-8800cceb52c1.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Miss Kelowna Lady of the Lake Society presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SUMMER NIGHTS GALA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Step back into the fabulous 50's for our Summer Nights Gala! Celebrate the journey of this year's Lady of the Lake candidates as they take the stage one final time before the crowning of the 2026 Kelowna Lady of the Lake Ambassadors. Enjoy an evening of entertainment, celebration, and community as we honour the confidence, leadership, and friendships built throughout the program.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $40.00</span>  ($32.42 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.22 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Summer Nights Gala</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
