  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Passion of Amy Winehouse";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/d9a0c32a-e9bd-4f3e-80d4-0c16be1d359b.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>LMS Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE PASSION OF AMY WINEHOUSE - BACK TO BLACK</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">featuring Heidi Munro</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The music, energy and optic of this performance will ignite a love and nostalgia for the songs of the incredible Amy Winehouse. Capturing the essence of Amy, this production features widely known and multi awarded Saskatchewan vocalist/performer, Heidi Munro. “The Passion of Amy Winehouse is performed with a stellar A-list of musicians well known across Canada.”<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This performance is a celebration of a gifted and raw artist in the truest form, as a songwriter, vocalist, performer and driven young woman. Heidi’s trademark “no holds barred” vocal style and passion lends itself to the depth of Amy’s honest, controversial, brilliant, and beautiful artistry, which is beyond what many can understand. Many of Amy’s jazz and hip-hop-infused poetic songs of very raw personal reflection will be featured.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Heidi Munro's production of \"Back to Black\" tribute to Amy Winehouse was a show worthy of any stage in Las Vegas. - American Federation of Musicians 553<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $68.77</span>  ($57.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.66 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Passion of Amy Winehouse</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
