<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/385602AGDPMRRNHGGVTLSTGJPCLKCJLCP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "THE PRICE IS RIGHT LIVE - ON STAGE";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/123b026b-2194-4898-bedb-42abcd1da41f.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Paul Mercs Concerts Inc. presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE PRICE IS RIGHT LIVE - ON STAGE</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Come on Down” to THE PRICE IS RIGHT LIVE™, you could be next! This family-friendly show is making its way to you, get your tickets TODAY! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This isn’t just any stage show - it’s an interactive, non-televised, live version of the iconic game show you know and love, hosted by our larger-than-life Celebrity Host who brings all the fun, flair, and unforgettable personality you expect from The Price Is Right. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Watch as randomly selected contestants from the audience spin The Big Wheel™, drop chips on Plinko™, climb toward victory in Cliffhangers™, and even take a shot at the fabulous Showcase—all surrounded by the classic sets and energy you know and love. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With incredible prizes up for grabs—appliances, dream vacations, electronics, even a brand-new car—lucky audience members can win big without ever leaving their seats. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Have ever dreamt of spinning The Big Wheel™, now is your chance to come up on stage and try to land on ONE DOLLAR! Ready to meet our Celebrity Host? Hear first-hand stories and experience the history of The Price is Right! Check out our website for details on special packages that are available now! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For over 20 years, fans across America have packed the house, winning over $15 million in prizes, and now it’s your turn… So, grab your friends and your family, bring that big-game energy, and get ready to hear those three magic words…<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>COME… ON… DOWN! The next contestant could be YOU! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This is a strict no cameras/no video event.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This is an all-ages event, however patrons must be 19+ if they wish to register to be a contestant.</span></span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $111.32</span>  ($94.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $14.21 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $71.65</span>  ($60.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.04 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3  $53.82</span>  ($44.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.71 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP Packages - limited availablity!</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP 1 Meet & Greet Experience Package  $255.07</span> ($219.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $32.96 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Meet & Greet Experience Package Includes:<span><br/></span>● One Premium Reserved Ticket Located In The First (5) Rows <span><br/></span>● Pre-Show Photo Meet & Greet with Host & Price Is Right Live Model (Your camera) <span><br/></span>● Fast Access to Check-In (does not influence contestant selection) <span><br/></span>● Exclusive The Price Is Right Laminate <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP 2 Spin The Big Wheel Package  $214.82</span>  ($184.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $27.71 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Spin The Big Wheel Package Includes:<span><br/></span>● One Premium Reserved Ticket Located In The First (15) Rows <span><br/></span>● Spin The Big Wheel! (After the show) <span><br/></span>● Official Photograph with The Big Wheel (Your camera) <span><br/></span>● Fast Access to Check-In (does not influence contestant selection) <span><br/></span>● Exclusive The Price Is Right Laminate <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Price Is Right Live - On Stage</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
