			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b8a8e91c-6b27-46b4-a915-0c825d37c9d5.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>New Vintage Theatre presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE WATCHER IN THE WOODS</span> </h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This performance is for audiences age 12 and up, horror content.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This new spin on a terrifying 1980's classic is brought to the Black Box Theatre for two shows only. Featuring a cast of talented teen performers, this is the perfect show for teens and adults alike to indulge their hunger for a live summer horror experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">General  $17.63</span>  ($15.00 base price + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Watcher in the Woods</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
