une 29<span><br/></span>A high‑energy beach party meets cocktail experience, featuring great food, drinks, music, and a relaxed Okanagan vibe<span><br/></span>An ideal setting for client entertainment or team celebration<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This represents significant added value, particularly given the sold‑out status of the BC Lions games and the limited availability of remaining inventory.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Corporate Passport*  $3148.95</span>  ($2999.00 base price + $149.95 GST)<span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Corporate Passports</span> and their applicable taxes are non-refundable.</span>
