<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/388001ABDHJGLRKGDQTGGQBQMNHCSNHTS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Wheeler Walker Jr. - Pullin' Out: The Farewell Tour";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/5915da85-7b66-42f2-b752-e7318b07e071.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Live Nation presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">WHEELER WALKER JR</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Pullin' Out: The Farewell Tour</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This event is restricted to patrons aged 19 and over.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Wheeler Walker Jr. brings his farewell tour to Kelowna Community Theatre for one final night of his signature country parody.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Created by comedian Ben Hoffman, the Wheeler Walker Jr. persona built a devoted following by blending traditional country sounds with bold, irreverent comedy. His performances include explicit language and adult themes and are intended strictly for mature audiences. Audience discretion is strongly advised.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Love him or hate him, the character has become one of the most talked-about acts in modern country satire—racking up chart success, massive streaming numbers, and a loyal cult following along the way. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>True to form, he’s not exiting quietly, offering one last round of his boundary-pushing take on country music before closing the curtain on the project. This is your last chance to see the act live.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Limited VIP packages are available, including a pre-show acoustic performance and roast, an exclusive merch item, a collectable Farewell Tour laminate, and early merch access.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $69.91</span>  ($57.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.55 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $58.41</span>  ($47.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.05 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><span class=\"UnderlineText\">VIP Package - The Wheeler Walker Jr. Pre-Show Acoustic Roast</span></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$281.81</span>  ($243.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $36.45 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Includes:<span><br/></span>  - One (1) VIP Reserved ticket<span><br/></span>  - Exclusive access to pre-show acoustic performance & roast by Wheeler Walker Jr.<span><br/></span>  - Exclusive Merch Item<span><br/></span>  - Commemmorative VIP Laminate<span><br/></span>  - First Access to merch shopping<span><br/></span>  - First Entry at Doors<span><br/></span>  - Limited number of packages available!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Wheeler Walker Jr.</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
