<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/386801ARPMDNKJGRLJPRRMLKKTHBSQNLQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Wilder Voices";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/7a4ccd3f-2c19-4377-9e37-8785f084273f.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>The Wilder Institute presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">WILDER VOICES</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The future of the wild is being written right now.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us in Kelowna on September 22 for the Wilder Voices Speaker Series featuring award-winning conservationist Brian Keating. Through compelling stories and thoughtful conversation, this special evening will explore the urgent need to protect wildlife and their habitats while highlighting the conservation work being advanced by the Wilder Institute and its partners in Canada and around the world.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Designed to foster meaningful community engagement, Wilder Voices offers an inspiring and educational experience that connects you to the heart of our mission and the collective effort required to create lasting change for wildlife and people.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Help us build one wild future — a future where wildlife and people thrive, together.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Applicable ticket fees for <span class=\"BoldText\">Wilder Voices</span> are non-refundable.</span>
""";
